# Alternative structure for hub/main menu scene
Main (Node)
├─ GameManager (Node)
├─ UIManager (Node)
├─ AudioManager (Node)
├─ CanvasLayer (UI layer)
│   ├─ DimBackground
│   ├─ PopupLayer → PopupManager
│   ├─ MainMenuUI (if you have one)
│   ├─ GachaUI
│   ├─ InventoryUI
│   └─ CampfireUI
└─ GameViewport (SubViewport or Node2D for actual gameplay)
    └─ Camera2D

